title: Phish - "Greetings From Coney Island In Brooklyn New York&q
description:
"Greetings From Coney Island In Brooklyn New York" - Phish

1. Camel Walk

2. Stash

3. Cars Trucks Buses

4. Tweezer

5. Chalk Dust Torture

6. A Song I Heard the Ocean Sing

7. Undermind

8. Crowd Control

This is a promotional maxi-single that came with pre-orders of the Phish:Live in Brooklyn DVD. 

All tracks recorded live June 17-18, 2004 at Keyspan Park, Brooklyn, New York. The last three songs were played at the soundcheck on June 17th and the first five played live on the 18th.
